      <text xml:space="preserve">{{For|the documentary film|Albert Schweitzer (film)}}
{{Infobox scientist
| name              = Albert Schweitzer
| image             = Bundesarchiv Bild 183-D0116-0041-019, Albert Schweitzer.jpg
