      <minor />
      <comment>/* References */ narrow cat</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox medical person
|name                    =Alexis Carrel
|image                   =Alexis Carrel 02.jpg
|caption                 =
|birth_date              =June 28, 1873 
|birth_place             =[[Sainte-Foy-lès-Lyon]], [[Rhône (department)|Rhône]], [[France]]
|death_date              ={{death date and age|1944|11|5|1873|6|28}}
|death_place             =  
|profession              =[[Surgeon]], [[Biologist]]
|specialism              = [[transplantology]], [[thoracic surgery]]
|religion                = [[Catholic Church|Roman Catholicism]]
|research_field          =
|known_for               = New techniques in [[Blood vessel|vascular]] sutures and  pioneering work in transplantology and thoracic surgery.
