      <text xml:space="preserve">[[Image:Antigua-Barbuda-demography.png|thumb|300px|right|Demographics of Antigua and Barbuda, Data of [[FAO]], year 2005 ; Number of inhabitants in thousands.]]

This article is about the [[demographics|demographic]] features of the [[population]] of [[Antigua and Barbuda]], including [[population density]], [[Ethnic group|ethnicity]], education level, health of the populace, economic status, religious affiliations and other aspects of the population.

==Demographic statistics from the CIA World Factbook==
[[Image:Antigua and Barbuda population pyramid 2005.png|thumb|300px|[[Population pyramid]]]]

The following demographic statistics are from the [[CIA World Factbook]], unless otherwise indicated.

