[[Image:Satellite image of Azerbaijan in March 2003.jpg|thumb|left|300px|NASA satellite image of Azerbaijan.]]
[[Image:Flooding in Azerbaijan.jpg|thumb|left|300px|Subtle changes due to rising sea level can be seen along this coastline]]

'''[[Azerbaijan]]''' is situated in the [[Caucasus]] region of [[Eurasia]].  Three physical features dominate Azerbaijan: the [[Caspian Sea]], whose shoreline forms a natural boundary to the east; the [[Greater Caucasus]] mountain range to the north; and the extensive flatlands at the country's center. About the size of [[Portugal]] or the state of [[Maine]], Azerbaijan has a total land